{"word":"θρόος","slug":"θρόος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>θρόος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θρέομαι'><el>θρέομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a noise</i> as of many voices, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; of musical sounds, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>the murmuring</i> of a crowd, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a report</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>rumor</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}